{"tid":1387661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"試着說：香港人，不要說：後生仔/示威者","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:50:49.000Z","uid":144187,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0fb46667a1f250193de4cf5bd4542be91b61a3","tid":1387661,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"有個心理學家話，我地錯曬喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n正如呢篇文所講嘅一樣，我地要做到團結不分化嘅第一步，就係要唔好標籤咗大家。<br />\n<br />\n只有大家都覺得自己係「香港人」，先會願意接受大家嘅幫助，願意一齊罷工，保衛我地嘅家園。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<code>光復香港 時代革命</code><br />\n<code>陪審團行使否決權無須理由</code>"},{"pid":"f6e9abc5526f695e8462d291bf284dcc00f16a09","tid":1387661,"uid":144187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"818eed253ea81a18800c76bad8be6a6d0168c9bc","tid":1387661,"uid":144187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8accbe5ad8d76bb5f93e9eafe5f41273c0db64b3","tid":1387661,"uid":144187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fc2f8c648cd4eb6f36906a9b18c8d6b007f19a36","tid":1387661,"uid":144187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a646812a0fae5cfbac7b677db6a6928f1251034c","tid":1387661,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44070c804e4186e0f256f9a37c83989ea4a627ad","tid":1387661,"uid":144187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"06b132f83ef47d0b650ddde23bea48f3b30c7145","tid":1387661,"uid":206421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:51:15.000Z